# Messages file for sampler
_TaskName:Sampler

# Standard miscellaneous messages
reportt:Message from Sampler
StatusIdle:Idle
StatusRecording:Recording
StatusPlaying:Playing
StatusPausedRecording:Paused during recording
StatusPausedPlaying:Paused during playback

# Error messages
NotEnoughMemory:There is not enough memory to do that operation.
CreateFirst:Before recording you must create the file which the sample will be saved to. Do this by clicking on the filename pop-up in the Record window.
WrongFiletype:The file you are trying to save to is not the correct type. Before trying to begin recording, you should create a file using the filename pop-up in the Record window.
NoPlaybackName:You need to specify the name of the sample to playback. To do this, drag a sample onto the sampler window or the icon bar icon.
WrongPlaybackType:The file you are trying to playback is an unrecognised type.
FileNotExist:The file you are trying to playback doesn't exist!
CantPlayBusy:You can't start playing until you stop the current sample.
CantRecordBusy:You can't start recording until you stop the current sample.
NoPlayWhileRecord:You must stop recording before trying to playback a sample.
